(76, '1118413039', '1118413039', '7755 7th Street', '92371', '', '7th', 'Phelan', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 2.0, '98160', 2, 'One', 500000, 2009, '2026-04-02 07:45:05', '2025-06-25', 34.466182000000000, -117.493337000000000, 'Caleb', 'Blasius', 'Active', 'RE/MAX FREEDOM', 'Modern 4-Bedroom Home on 2.5-Acre Horse Property with Equestrian Features and Mountain Views\r\r\nIntroducing a well-maintained single-story home situated on approximately 2.5 acres, offering a unique opportunity for equestrian use and rural living. Built in 2020, this 2,007 sq. ft. residence features 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and is designed with both functionality and comfort in mind.\r\r\nThe open-concept layout includes vaulted ceilings and a spacious kitchen equipped with custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and recessed lighting. The living area includes a fireplace with a raised hearth, ideal for a cozy atmosphere. The primary suite offers a large walk-in closet, dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a walk-in shower. Three additional bedrooms are located on the opposite wing of the home, along with a full guest bathroom. Other interior features include luxury vinyl plank and tile flooring, mirrored closet doors, a finished garage, a dedicated laundry room with storage, and a tankless water heater.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413039\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTE0MTE4OA\\/oCcAWU5hxDstWRbWCgem43CJW7_2MNkzx6WlAOxeku0\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413039\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTE0MTE4OA\\/Y-NaPsar0neAy-HtJDjIqkVyh0uTFbPmYGEHY1_QtVU\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413039\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTE0MTE4OA\\/4cENEmbkc1RragFjkHcQFb4bIV41QCLobN4knE5vTrw\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413039\\/