(106, '1119757884', '1119757884', '13679 Calle Romano', '22106', '', 'Calle Romano', 'Tijuana', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 4.0, '2637', 2, 'ThreeOrMore', 480000, 2637, '2025-07-22 12:07:40', '2025-06-24', 32.484501290000000, -116.975017160000000, 'Juan Antonio', 'Escorcia Cervantes', 'Active', 'ROA California Inc', 'Introducing Helena Residences, an exclusive development of eight luxury homes currently under construction in one of Tijuana’s most strategically located areas. Situated just one minute from Boulevard Díaz Ordaz, this project offers a rare combination of privacy, modern design, and accessibility.  Each residence is designed with meticulous attention to detail and built with premium materials. Interior features include Travertine marble floors, luxury-grade finishes, high-end kitchens equipped with a pantry, integrated LED lighting, and air conditioning ductwork prepared throughout the home. The homes are thoughtfully distributed across multiple levels, offering up to four bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms. The principal suite includes a walk-in closet and a private terrace, providing an ideal retreat space.  Residents will enjoy architectural elements that enhance both comfort and style. These include a private lobby entrance, an interior garden, full sliding glass doors for natural integration between indoor and outdoor spaces, and expansive living areas perfect for family gatherings or entertaining guests. Additional features include two generous parking spaces, natural lighting in stairways, elevated doors measuring 2.40 meters, and a landscaped roof garden with the option of a fourth bedroom and full bathroom on the top floor.  The community is designed for privacy and security, featuring wide central streets, direct access from Avenida Romano, CCTV surveillance, and remote-controlled access gates.  Prices start at $480,000 USD. Additionally, financing options are available to assist buyers in securing their ideal residence within this exclusive project.  Now is the ideal time to take advantage of this opportunity while the project remains under construction. For more information or to schedule a private consultation, feel free to contact us directly.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/iRsELGzNJCPzxk17cmuLrMxP-1w9Tpxp_l2BWP2JDrs\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/HJN5zksVAMMrDIjH-CBpUp73Ekrwhi0kEfMrFSrGJps\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/SeAaeATMB046v_PyfZFfBI097hZfYGZJ2Ndg-L2BrM0\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/D6K7Lcl_blOUdOZHJDIIhax70Jg_bIxgLwjn4M9YB6Y\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/We84_kyipn5hM3OvuL6jV5HwtyDuIi1SDMO0PUHwOGg\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/V6ZFHp9SVoXV23nYlDw0VLT8455l42b_6lxNaGEWibw\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/MTYfHqQz3z4Jdfn6QLknMcdFn8sQmg6l3zDiZ4icbdw\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/3J-5BdiDUnLPcN8fmn1FLzjidhc5OiI9Tni6rp7hzpc\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1119757884\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/pbk9VsaX2qpub5vS90kVp83K9VwIcHplxIZ2E438_zA\",\"https