(170, '1118404445', '1118404445', '660 Sunfish Way', '93041', 'Surfside IIIC - 245903', 'Sunfish', 'Port Hueneme', 'CA', 'Residential', 'Condominium', 3, 2.0, NULL, 0, 'One', 625000, 1197, '2026-04-26 10:40:27', '2025-06-24', 34.142335000000000, -119.190175000000000, 'Kiran', 'Locke', 'Active', 'Surfside-Anacapa Real Estate', 'MAJOR PRICE REDUCTION!!!! Very motivated sellers!!!Welcome to this stunningly renovated single-story corner unit in the highly desirable gated Surfside III community of Port Hueneme. This 3BR/2BA condo has been fully upgraded from floor to ceiling, combining modern finishes with the laid-back charm of beachside living.Located on the quiet end of the building with no steps, this ground-floor unit offers 2 balconies with views of bubbling springs, lush greenery, and peekaboo ocean views--a rare blend of privacy and natural beauty.Inside, enjoy luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, an open-concept layout, and a remodeled kitchen featuring quartz countertops, soft-close cabinets and drawers, stainless steel appliances, and an added peninsula with extra storage and space for entertaining.The spacious primary suite includes access to the balcony patio and an attached bath with a shower-over-tub combination. The guest bedrooms are located in a separate wing, offering privacy and easy access to a second bathroom with a modern shower stall and separated powder area.Surfside III offers an impressive array of resort-style amenities, including a clubhouse with a heated indoor pool, hot tub, and fitness center with cardio and strength-training equipment, a recreation area with pool table, ping pong, and foosball, outdoor BBQ and picnic areas, basketball and volleyball courts, and even an outdoor gymThis community is directly across from the beach with its own private gated beach access via a footbridge leading directly to the sand.Perfectly situated between Malibu and Santa Barbara, and just minutes from the Naval base, shopping, dining, and essential services, this condo offers an unbeatable lifestyle at a very affordable price for a spacious beachside home.Don\'t miss your chance to own a move-in-ready coastal retreat in a vibrant, amenity-rich community.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/uvIwO5NLr6NZcPdpHuGsCPw1iJx10znHq-TtLGLajqg\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/FrPhKRiKbprnXsmLbO4YN0S1MNaFRrQCh1KD1XQ-nh0\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/dKh8dl8ryJkUDO3MNQyXNvLqf6pLqac9yKWcJiSC7_4\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/wuTWiUN-2_ASDgBOimCIJxT9sojSTJm5d2pwuD2iAUQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/3iQOuiKIXpq5JF2XwqrgRtZcSCyyr8ndbLLD3ZW536A\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/xT4hddl50T_MbGF2uXTJxORG2R2QYhU7uaikPcew8fc\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/qpcVpvoIctwZfiurBm3j1190twFETL36dvDk-5gPOLg\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/h3geFu4lLp5VufhJOPAjHMJ6E-BPFfg0zsdazgBEnTQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzIyNTYyMw\\/bAe7Q7B944s2TBZPMaBPjQyygEpzjB3GCegKGZy31l8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118404445\\/10\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/Mj