(203, '1118391088', '1118391088', '455 E Ocean Boulevard 502', '90802', '', 'Ocean', 'Long Beach', 'CA', 'Residential', 'Condominium', 1, 1.0, '19950', NULL, 'One', 484900, 1029, '2026-04-13 10:42:35', '2025-06-24', 33.767004000000000, -118.186661000000000, 'Oliver', 'Moussazadeh', 'Active', 'Revilo Realty, Inc.', '** BEST DEAL IN THE BUILDING ! ** Fantastic Corner Unit in The Historic Cooper Arms Building on Ocean Boulevard in the Heart of Downtown Long Beach! Featuring an open modern-concept layout w/ breathtaking panoramic views of the city to the bay, this spacious 5th floor unit has oversized newer dual-pane windows w/ lots of natural light & wood parquet flooring throughout. Living room w/ ceiling fan & built-ins. Adjacent dining area w/ chandelier. Balcony w/ fantastic panoramic views - the perfect place for a morning coffee or afternoon cocktail! Upgraded kitchen w/ stone countertops, designer backsplash, & dine-in bar. Exposed wood-beam ceilings & brick walls throughout. Spacious bedroom w/ remodeled bathroom. 2 large cedar-lined walk-in closets w/ abundant storage. Building amenities include controlled access, on-site management, secure package lockers, bike storage, community laundry in the basement, courtyard w/ BBQ & picnic area, main level Grand Salon & top floor solarium. Walking distance to the shoreline & the best shopping, dining, & entertainment the area has to offer. A unique opportunity to own a piece of history in one of the best locations in the city!', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118391088\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjEwMjY4Ng\\/iG3st9QBMINTuD7uMICH0UMhuIoOzwCyiB0Sf_04P0E\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118391088\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjEwMjY4Ng\\/VYkd90xNM1VIAHCCmxW003cP9oZiA-4vpra2JB6jrE4\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118391088\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMT