(214, '1118389973', '1118389973', '9904 Kip Drive', '90210', '', 'Kip', 'Beverly Hills', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 10, 22.0, '860310', NULL, 'ThreeOrMore', 79000000, 24757, '2025-07-02 05:21:34', '2025-06-24', 34.101279000000000, -118.432962000000000, 'Kurt', 'Rappaport', 'Active', 'Westside Estate Agency Inc.', 'Set on nearly 20 acres behind a long private gated drive, overlooking spectacular city views, this stunning Contemporary Mediterranean Villa captures the warmth and beauty of Southern California living. This property defies description with over 25,000+ sq ft, 7 bedrooms, 13 full baths & 9 half baths, 9 fireplaces, an elevator, garage & motor court to accommodate 15 cars, staff quarters offering 3 bedrooms & separate full kitchen. The interiors have been designed for modern lifestyles, yet pay homage to timeless European elegance, which include a formal living room, dining room, library, commercial-grade gourmet kitchen, breakfast nook, family room, gym, game room, projection screening room, wine cellar & dining room. Offering a perfect setting for an outdoor soiree, the grounds inspire the kind of serenity found in the world\'s most secluded villas w/ immaculate lawns & gardens, orchards, fountains, a mosaic-tiled swimming pool, outdoor pavilion, pool house w/ kitchen & pizza oven, tennis court & pavilion, walking paths & a view to envy.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118389973\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/I4RBdpkf8CoGLE9NI4mNI2SOsKrVj3Xq-MLF70H0r6s\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118389973\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/RBKxBV4XJn0Dw_tDiYg3x_uXcq6tI8LZldeiZ1sejR8\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118389973\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5NjgxMQ\\/Up5GA-Pizj6ldjFzAf3609R2FNG98--hvI9w49VOSeg\",\"https:\\/\\/api-tre