(232, '1118383115', '1118383115', '14947 Dickens Street 3', '91403', '', 'Dickens', 'Sherman Oaks', 'CA', 'Residential', 'Townhouse', 2, 2.0, '9509', 2, 'Two', 750000, 1225, '2026-04-12 10:12:46', '2025-06-24', 34.151736000000000, -118.459065000000000, 'Jeff', 'Schermer', 'Active', 'Rodeo Realty', 'WOW! NOW REDUCED! California Living at its finest in this updated townhouse, just south of the famed Ventura Blvd with all its shopping and fine restaurants! The gated security entrance leads you to this cozy 8 unit boutique building offering a quieter more community-like feel than a larger complex. AND, a lower than normal  monthly HOA fee. The double door entry opens to light and airy floor plan with laundry IN THE UNIT! The living room and dining area boasts easy to care for Italian woodgrain tile and newer recessed lighting; it\'s warmed by the fireplace and feeds out to the private patio via the sliding glass door and its plantation shutters. The updated kitchen with newer appliances and fixtures, and ample granite counters will make any home-chef happy! The downstairs powder room has a new toilet and new fixtures. Primary Bedroom #1 contains a sizable walk-in closet. The larger Primary Bedroom #2 also has more than ample closet space. The main bathroom has been updated with an oversized tub and chic fixtures. In the rear of the complex lies a unique paved backyard perfect for BBQ\'s or social gatherings. Don\'t forget the  VERY LOW HOA!', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118383115\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjAxNTM1NQ\\/nfDImtraDFRiuf7LpJOBAtgn86AqXXyPgbyXfQgTKFA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118383115\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjAxNTM1NQ\\/3zCyBVvgS1pjFTBjSbT2R8k104-qhqMUu5CfYkqD81Y\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118383115\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjAxNTM1NQ\\/5PkKlPX1JXDqHQdUUTVcD6r