(305, '1118680851', '1118680851', '43539 Corte Del Oro', '92253', 'Esplanade', 'Corte Del Oro', 'La Quinta', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 2.0, '8712', 2, 'One', 625000, 2112, '2026-04-24 12:15:06', '2025-06-23', 33.732390000000000, -116.271254000000000, 'John Sloan', 'Real Estate Group...', 'Active', 'Keller Williams Realty', 'Welcome to Corte Del Oro in the sought-after Esplanade development inLa Quinta where comfort, convenience, and charm converge. This well-maintained home sits on an elevated lot with sweeping southwest-facing views of the mountains and lush greenbelt. Inside, you\'ll find three spacious bedrooms plus a den, that can also be used as a bedroom, a cozy fireplace in the living room, and a newer water heater already in place. Step outside and enjoy the Alumawood awning with manual shadesa\'perfect for relaxing afternoons or entertaining friends. With a two-car garage and being mostly furnished, this home is ready for you to move in and make it your own. Just minutes from shopping and dining at Fred Waring and Jefferson, and only 8 minutes to major retail centers. La Quinta is truly the gem of the desert and this home lets you experience it all.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118680851\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzA1OTk5Ng\\/VXYdPvbE5kfqRtIQzV65CXIXTuUK9hOQekah_lt_baY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118680851\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzA1OTk5Ng\\/cPJtW9FwwEPcbNHx8y3fuCZmq8c2wbOC1mozxPX4pts\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118680851\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzA1OTk5Ng\\/K3QidSKq1YZFx6uyDut_m7atKBRBBW3GFzMQ_PpgIYA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118680851\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzA1OTk5Ng\\/07hkG5_kHE_zkyfN1AeaEbzVirwt7Lz1rGbBXolIUnw\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/P