(316, '1118498224', '1118498224', '1206 Coast Oak Trail', '91906', '', 'Coast Oak', 'Campo', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 2.0, '0.12', 2, 'One', 400000, 1879, '2026-03-10 07:00:44', '2025-06-23', 32.617796000000000, -116.461989000000000, 'Collette', 'Jimenez', 'Active', 'Century 21 Affiliated', 'Escape to Peaceful Perfection in Campo, CA  Welcome to your sanctuary in the scenic countryside of Campo, California—where golden meadows meet rolling mountains and every day begins with expansive open skies. This beautifully designed single-level 4-bedroom, 2-bath home rests gracefully on a corner lot near the end of a quiet lane in the serene, gated community of Campo Hills. With no neighbors behind and just one beside, this is rural tranquility at its finest.  Step inside to discover lofty vaulted ceilings and an airy open layout that invites both relaxation and togetherness. A cozy fireplace anchors the living space, while the generously sized kitchen and dining area offer the perfect setting for slow breakfasts or heartfelt gatherings. The private primary suite is a restful retreat all its own, featuring a spa-inspired ensuite bath with soaking tub, dual vanities, a walk-in shower, and an expansive walk-in closet.  ?? Step outside to your own private slice of nature—where a fully fenced backyard and peaceful patio become your front-row seat to Campo’s quiet charm. Morning coffee under blue skies or evening conversations beneath the stars? Absolutely.  The Campo Hills community weaves energy-efficient living with thoughtful amenities like RV parking, a sparkling pool and spa, a playground, and a park-like picnic area with BBQs—adding comfort without compromising the rural calm. With low HOA fees and unmatched views, this is where simple living meets natural beauty.  Breathe deeply, unwind fully—this is life in Campo.  Heavy fixer with lots of potential.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118498224\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MzE1MTM4Nw\\/_grMIbzETUtWVZSRA28eEsBrvHUORr6tqP_d70P3B78\"]', '2025-06-27 11:25:44', 1, NULL, '1', '', 256, 'Monthly', '', '', 2008, '1', NULL, NULL, 'Mountain Empire Unified', 135, NULL, '2026-03-10 14:03:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, NULL, 'Assessor', 'Acres', NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 'Dryer,Washer', 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 256, 256, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 400000, 0.1200, 5227.20, 0.12, '2025-06-26 10:00:00', NULL, '2025-06-26 10:00:00', '2025-06-26 18:32:10', '2025-06-27', NULL, '2026-03-10', '619-471-2000', 'broker@century21award.com', 'collette.realtor@gmail.com', '619-838-1696', 'PacificSouthwest', 'Collette Jimenez', '', '17283775', '6551520100', 'urn:reso:upi:2.0:US:06073:6551520100', NULL, 'San Diego', 'CAMPO', '06073', 'Campo Hills', NULL, 'Barbecue,PicnicArea,Playground,Pool,RvParking', NULL, 'NoCommonWalls', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 'Active', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CentralAir', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Canyon,Mountains,Neighborhood,Rocks,Valley,TreesWoods', 'LivingRoom', 'ShortSale', 'AllBedroomsDown,Attic,BedroomOnMainLevel,EntranceFoyer,MainLevelPrimary,PrimarySuite,WalkInClosets', NULL, 'Community,Fenced,InGround,Association', 'Biking,Curbs,Fishing,Gutters,Hiking,HorseTrails,Hunting,Lake,MilitaryLand,Mountainous,NearNationalForest,Park,PreservePublicLand,Rural,Ravine,StreetLights,Suburban,Sidewalks,Valley,WaterSports,Pool', NULL, NULL, 'ZeroToOneUnitAcre,CornerLot,FrontYard,SprinklersInFront,Lawn,Landscaped,Level,Paved,RectangularLot,StreetLevel,Walkstreet,Yard', 'Cash', NULL, '1', 'Owner', 'Attic,Bedroom,EntryFoyer,Foyer,Kitchen,Laundry,LivingRoom,PrimaryBathroom,PrimaryBedroom,Other', '2025-06-27 05:25:44'),
