(380, '1118353931', '1118353931', '32753 State Highway 74', '92545', '', 'State Highway 74', 'Hemet', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 2.0, '180338', 0, 'One', 625000, 1482, '2025-08-05 16:30:10', '2025-06-23', 33.737066000000000, -117.089248000000000, 'Jessica', 'Francia', 'Active', 'Vylla Home, Inc.', 'RANCH PROPERTY – 4.14 ACRES! 2 HOMES ON TOP!\r\r\nFlat, fully usable, and fenced land ideally located just off State Highway 74 and minutes from the 215 Freeway. Situated in the sought-after \"Green Acres\" area, this property features cross-fenced pastures and 5 horse stalls with water access. Improvements include a 3-bedroom, 1-bath main home and a single-wide mobile home with 1 bedroom and 1 bath. Utilities include separate SoCal Gas and Edison meters, two septic systems, city water, and a private well. Incredible potential for a ranch, RV park, nursery, or a range of agricultural or residential uses. Buyer to perform their own due diligence.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353931\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njg2NA\\/jp6KmVmmuozckhSpXus4UJ-Ml81mshYKwIge4W0A9gc\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353931\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njg2NA\\/FA64XL-6eshODnO_SwjXxzRDtnJyk2dRnLHUz6LX2CI\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353931\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njg2NA\\/v9N1iHwodnLt7nf7Cxn63k5cqtL4w02FVtvyLO-Xxgc\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353931\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njg2NA\\/D9zKxzYlqfch5iLA2oRIqgZI4PJyfGAprbK9QdE8n8w\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353931\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njg2NA\\/i5oeagZ4QTHlHTZfDdw1fqqHPwBAwRZOllzXkrWEsR8\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/tre