(384, '1118353294', '1118353294', '350 S. Fairway Dr', '92352', 'Arrowhead Woods (AWHW)', 'S. Fairway Dr', 'Lake Arrowhead', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 2.0, '8400', 0, 'ThreeOrMore', 599000, 1732, '2026-04-23 11:29:07', '2025-06-23', 34.247125000000000, -117.222546000000000, 'GAILMARIE', 'BRAMLETT', 'Active', 'THE GM GROUP', 'Wrapped in pines and rich with character, this vintage A-frame brings together iconic mountain design, tasteful updates, and the lifestyle Lake Arrowhead buyers are searching for. The flat-faced prow, bold roofline, and redwood fencing give the home striking presence, while soaring wood-beam ceilings, dramatic triangular windows, and a classic stone fireplace create a warm, unforgettable interior. The open dining area connects naturally to the updated kitchen with open shelving and warm wood accents, while upstairs, a spacious loft-style game room offers added room to gather, unwind, or host guests. Beautifully updated bathrooms introduce fresh modern finishes without losing the home’s rustic charm. A seasonal creek enhances the serene setting, and central A/C adds comfort throughout the year. Outside, the deck is perfectly positioned to enjoy the wooded surroundings, mature trees, and fresh alpine air. Complete with Lake Rights, rare level entry, private lake access, and a strong short-term rental history, this is a distinctive mountain escape with lasting appeal.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353294\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3Njk3MTI0Mw\\/-CVvPLWrMc-ymhAT81IYq8evUx-cBAPcT0LkBhApmy8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353294\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3Njk3MTI0Mw\\/_YBziZ-cLBheKq4sgX-GNz4ztadYqDMmrpy0UELRtbY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118353294\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3Njk3MTI0Mw\\/XaKA-5kZtOmuRVOUazI0lWTVJOjdI2aa1QCyFfhFnlM\",\"http