(529, '1118311302', '1118311302', '5963 Rio Valle Drive', '92003', 'Bonsall', 'Rio Valle', 'Bonsall', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 3.0, '14810', 2, 'Two', 1084999, 2329, '2026-03-26 12:42:31', '2025-06-22', 33.294331000000000, -117.226031000000000, 'Maurice', 'Watkins', 'Active', 'Allison James Estates & Homes', 'Designed with comfort and functionality in mind, this home welcomes you with dramatic ceilings and an airy layout that invites natural light into every corner. Whether you\'re hosting a formal dinner or enjoying a cozy evening with family, the versatile living and dining areas offer the ideal backdrop.\r\r\nThe kitchen is a showstopper. It is modern, sleek, and loaded with storage. With gleaming granite counters, stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinetry, and dual pantries, this space makes everyday cooking feel like a culinary adventure. A generously sized family room serves as the heart of the home—perfect for movie nights, celebrations, or simply relaxing. Guests will appreciate the privacy and ease of a downstairs bedroom and full bath, tucked away from the main living areas. Upstairs, retreat to a spacious primary suite that feels more like a personal sanctuary. There’s room for everything—an office, a yoga mat, or your favorite reading chair. Step out onto the private balcony and take in peaceful backyard views. The spa-inspired bathroom features a soaking tub, separate shower, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet ready for your wardrobe. The outdoor space is just as impressive. Fire up the grill in the built-in kitchen, dine under the covered patio with ceiling fans, or let kids and pets play freely on the grassy lawn. There’s also a large shed for your tools or hobbies, and plenty of space if you dream of adding a pool. Mature trees offer shade and charm, while dedicated RV or boat parking and a 3-car garage provide practicality without sacrificing curb appeal. Located in one of North County’s most peaceful pockets, Bonsall blends country charm with modern convenience—rolling vineyards, equestrian trails, and top-rated schools, all just a short drive from the beach, shopping, and freeways.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/JNQqtfllikCbXMObBFaR40b_HNh23l5z8hNxhMLJyss\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/G8NSu0Zclt5LC3liDPIR4dfRs1WcLbdA19QJUQfSfJk\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/3AJelE50AQhYGCa6Tp1lMmmKrCgbGeIfbCdst-3XH5g\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/yaW8XtVOuc-dpOWe5dMSNNZYzXx3vAnm9F03_nfootQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/DidtrLs3nhbKlFvrhsZ5X56-8t92-TVWk8jKAGloTrI\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/WasNvlXRlF67IF2FL37H-g9mcc6pvcs8idowvpYZnw8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/JdLBRkAJqMEGBLSRwSVoweDd_cn2Vx-S2hAGriEPOxM\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/pvMVfhnPFRZKG71uzf6VVjCMu0HCFyw9geHLEz0VDws\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/6KRIeRuiaNYDQ6jOMap7pEUYuHg6GSBMC_NczbZ7Vnk\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118311302\\/10\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NDU1NDM2Nw\\/FFK9wA_HAxx