(673, '1118296285', '1118296285', '1129 Via Mirabel', '90274', '', 'Via Mirabel', 'Palos Verdes Estates', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 13, 20.0, '143392', 8, 'ThreeOrMore', 28888000, 34143, '2026-04-25 13:09:54', '2025-06-20', 33.789423000000000, -118.399037000000000, 'Bryn', 'Stroyke', 'Active', 'Bayside', 'Set behind gates on the largest and most private parcel in Palos Verdes Estates, this extraordinary 3.3-acre compound presents a once-in-a-generation opportunity to own and reimagine one of the largest residential estates in all of Southern California.\r\r\n\r\r\nSpanning over 34,000 square feet, the residence offers an unparalleled foundation of scale, volume, and infrastructure—features that would be extraordinarily difficult, if not impossible, to recreate today. Expansive grounds include a resort-sized pool, tennis court, multiple outdoor entertaining areas, and mature landscaping that provides complete privacy.\r\r\n\r\r\nOriginally designed with a global aesthetic and grand entertaining in mind, the home is defined by dramatic proportions, soaring ceilings, and an extensive layout that accommodates large-scale living, multi-generational use, or a world-class private compound.\r\r\n\r\r\nAmenities include multiple entertaining salons, a professional-grade kitchen with auxiliary prep spaces, wellness and recreational facilities, and significant support infrastructure including elevators, staff quarters, and an eight-car garage.\r\r\n\r\r\nFor the discerning buyer, this property represents a unique opportunity to modernize and curate a truly bespoke estate—leveraging irreplaceable land, scale, and privacy to create a legacy residence tailored to today’s standards.\r\r\n\r\r\nLocated within close proximity to Los Angeles while offering a level of seclusion rarely found, this is a property of exceptional potential and enduring value.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118296285\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw