(735, '1118282711', '1118282711', '2617 Sierra Street', '90031', '', 'Sierra', 'Los Angeles', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 5, 5.0, '7349', NULL, 'Two', 949900, 3131, '2026-02-22 10:27:42', '2025-06-20', 34.077140000000000, -118.201966000000000, 'Orit', 'Gadish', 'Active', 'Geffen Real Estate', 'Perched high in the hills of Lincoln Heights, this 5-bedroom, 4.5-bath modern retreat invites you to experience its elegance, ease, and panoramic views of the downtown skyline! Inside, gleaming tile floors guide you to an open-concept living and dining area, blending effortlessly into a kitchen defined by stainless appliances, minimalist cabinetry, and a honeycomb backsplash. Three bright bedrooms grace the main floor, while two more, along with a stylish family corner and kitchenette, await on the lower level, where glass sliders open to an expansive entertainer\'s patio. Your generous primary suite features vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, and a chic ensuite. A flexible bonus room, a laundry nook, and a studio ADU with its own kitchen and bath add everyday versatility. Whether hosting under the stars on your rooftop deck or unwinding on one of several serene terraces, the city feels just far enough away. Located only a short drive from Dodger Stadium, local schools, major freeways, and the vast array of leisure and shopping options of DTLA, come explore a lifestyle with elevated design!', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282711\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MTc4NTE3NA\\/fPHn6pP7vSNOxZJAjuIvRDTvo5ZEI3dD53z6i4maq1I\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282711\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MTc4NTE3NA\\/hmjrXAdFRBmdUeK7SskdG7vtg8jnM0U1CQORQA3lDfY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282711\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MTc4NTE3NA\\/D-qYjxz9CzzyyICkWoNwlHbhiURHEVuPNUAs83tK-qY\",\"https:\\/\\/ap