(737, '1118282477', '1118282477', '1094 Manzanita Avenue', '95926', '', 'Manzanita', 'Chico', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 2.0, '10019', 2, 'One', 540000, 1740, '2025-06-25 12:28:26', '2025-06-20', 39.753417000000000, -121.834142000000000, 'Michelle', 'Molina Weupe', 'Active', 'Coldwell Banker Select Real Estate', 'Welcome to 1094 Manzanita Avenue – a spacious and character-filled 1960\'s home nestled along the peaceful Lindo Channel in Chico! This beautifully maintained residence offers the perfect blend of vintage charm and modern upgrades. Step inside to find a stunning, updated kitchen and bathrooms featuring elegant marble countertops. The expansive front living room boasts gleaming hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, and abundant natural light.\r\r\nEnjoy a second, separate living area with a warm wood stove, custom built-ins, and striking beamed ceiling—perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The backyard is an entertainer’s dream, complete with custom concrete work, a gazebo with a built-in BBQ, bar seating, and an outdoor dining area. Double gates with RV parking. A lush lawn and an array of fruit trees—Meyer lemon, Fuji apple, and persimmon—add to the home\'s unique charm. Whether you\'re enjoying morning coffee with views of the Lindo Channel or hosting evening gatherings under the gazebo, this home offers comfort, beauty, and functionality in one of Chico’s most desirable locations.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282477\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njk4NQ\\/R2citu9XaXwA1GnRNaiUH_TGFUYcCCvSdidAg1nHOg4\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282477\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njk4NQ\\/IUG1G0xy_trClUAUuSu7KR70yaQq2FUldDiAgDi21xM\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118282477\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc1OTk5Njk4NQ\\/Y8TlMngPn0TZVeurGYDt7Q