(862, '1118534515', '1118534515', '7559 Midfield Avenue', '90045', '', 'Midfield', 'Los Angeles', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 3.0, '5668', 1, 'One', 1375000, 1579, '2026-01-06 14:42:16', '2025-06-19', 33.968456000000000, -118.374243000000000, 'Bill', 'Ruane', 'Active', 'Estate Properties', 'Welcome to 7559 Midfield Avenue, a beautifully renovated gem in the heart of Westchester. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home perfectly blends modern luxury with everyday comfort. The open-concept layout features dual living rooms that flow into a stylish dining area and chef-inspired kitchen, complete with a gas stove, high-end refrigerator, island, and ample cabinetry. Throughout the home, you\'ll find new vinyl flooring, recessed lighting, upgraded electrical, dimmable fan lights, and fresh paint, all contributing to a sleek, contemporary feel.\r\r\nStep outside to your own private retreat—completed in July 2021, the heated pool and spa are surrounded by lush landscaping and an inviting outdoor BBQ area, perfect for entertaining. Additional features include a fully equipped separate laundry room, a one-car garage, and a gated driveway with parking for two. With recent renovations inside and out, plus a five-year-old central AC/heat system, this home offers turnkey living in one of Westchester’s most sought-after neighborhoods.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118534515\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2Nzc0Nzc2OQ\\/uPcMT0D_4jnD_1zGH6nSmvvPBIMcgZE1JzeL16cm_Co\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118534515\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2Nzc0Nzc2OQ\\/AEwNWo2l0XUFCl4KO0EVJXvxyJFtFQLCXiTKu2BjxUo\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118534515\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2Nzc0Nzc2OQ\\/YSPn2wTs2n_8CG8ccn_xZCFqYkrbp2WFrjVOtJsWEnQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/111853