(866, '1118491590', '1118491590', '410 Los Angeles Avenue', '92386', '', 'Los Angeles', 'Sugarloaf', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 2.0, '5000', 0, 'One', 375000, 1309, '2026-04-27 09:42:58', '2025-06-19', 34.244724000000000, -116.833082000000000, 'RACHAEL', 'SMITH', 'Active', 'RE/MAX BIG BEAR', 'Your perfect slice of Big Bear living awaits! Step into this charming log-style cabin and feel the weight of the world melt away. The warm and inviting living room features a beautiful rock fireplace and soaring vaulted ceilings—ideal for snuggling up on crisp mountain evenings. Sunlight pours in through the many windows, filling the space with natural light. The kitchen is just the right size, complete with an adorable dining nook that adds to the home’s cozy appeal. The spacious primary suite includes a large bathroom and wide hallways that add to the open feel of the home. Start your mornings on the front deck, sipping coffee as you listen to the forest come alive, and spend your afternoons entertaining on the generous side deck. This is more than just a cabin—it’s where lifelong memories are made. Don’t let this mountain gem slip away! Used as a short term rental currently', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118491590\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzMwODIyOQ\\/g50FdRMpSgeTIZyCB0-Y1sPO1OcAm2JptlcybXgDSX8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118491590\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzMwODIyOQ\\/RwI-25_o0zMZhutaW5Dh6SpHfdTKCjr1fhB2z8zPY1I\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118491590\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzMwODIyOQ\\/fa5x9y96-2OP-7CFLl_CrNh4PQjAYuN8U6KUIVu-4as\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118491590\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NzMwODIyOQ\\/hqO1591Pe0NjX1zl4qCcsIP72-j1rauxO_k6V3AHv1U\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Med