(943, '1117764755', '1117764755', '21900 Parrott Ranch Road', '93924', '', 'Parrott Ranch', 'Carmel Valley', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 5, 4.0, '871200', 0, '', 1450000, 1692, '2026-04-14 08:52:41', '2025-06-19', 36.375596750000000, -121.603927960000000, 'Kathy', 'Baker', 'Active', 'Carmel Valley Realty Company', 'Wonderful private country property on 20 acres.  This fantastic property has plenty of spacious decks to enjoy the outstanding mountain and vineyard views.  The main house has cathedral ceilings and  a stunning 20 foot high stone fireplace.  The house features beautiful stained concrete floors, air conditioning and a great kitchen open to the living and dining area.  The property has a very private separate 450 square foot charming guest house and a separate beautiful 2 bedroom 750 square foot  hideaway house with private access.   On the property is a green house, a large fenced in vegetable and herb garden, storage barn, private well, bocci ball court and two carports with additional storage.  The houses and property have been lovingly cared for and are turn key.   The home has easy access off a paved road.  This country dream home is waiting for you just 25 minutes from the Carmel Valley Village and 45 minutes from Carmel by The Sea and the Monterey Airport.  The property is within the Carmel Unified School District.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117764755\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjE4MjM1MQ\\/3Bb_Vk7EFcdWJkEgO0qBR73RoEffMDhI8mwzkHOR2JI\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117764755\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjE4MjM1MQ\\/hlBw6doZl12d2gA55WfHVfeBCx1HrBJeKhxPpIIlZYI\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117764755\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NjE4MjM1MQ\\/560E5hs2YxIRzblW870D2fASfXcNWkmir-3Z8gJeh_w\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO