(965, '1117761978', '1117761978', '23 BLVD Prieto Azabache', '99999', 'Out Of Area', 'BLVD Prieto Azabache', 'Other', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 2, 1.0, '1959', 0, 'One', 85000, 495, '2026-02-01 20:09:30', '2025-06-19', 32.403996000000000, -116.978090000000000, 'David Thomas', 'Mejia', 'Active', 'David T. Mejia', 'Discover an unparalleled opportunity to own a brand-new, customizable home in Tijuana\'s burgeoning Vista Horizonte community, Sección 2, for a fraction of U.S. prices. This move-in ready, block-construction home presents a unique blank canvas, inviting you to install your own choice of kitchen, flooring, and paint to perfectly match your style and budget. As an amazing alternative to the high cost of American real estate, this property is not only a smart investment in a booming market but also a gateway to an incredible lifestyle, located just a short drive from the vibrant culture of downtown Tijuana, the famous lobster village of Puerto Nuevo, the beautiful shores of Rosarito Beach, and the world-class wineries of the Guadalupe Valley. Best of all, this amazing opportunity is fully financeable through accessible government assistance programs like INFONAVIT and URBI, making your dream of new home ownership in Mexico an achievable reality.  Of course. I understand that using coordinates isn\'t practical for a property description. I\'ve removed them and refined the description to be more user-friendly while still highlighting the excellent location you wanted to showcase. Here is the revised property description:  Your Gateway to a New Home: Unbeatable Value in Tijuana\'s Vista Horizonte TIJUANA, BAJA CALIFORNIA – Imagine owning a brand-new home, a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch, for a fraction of the cost of a comparable property in the United States. This exceptional opportunity is now a reality in the burgeoning community of Vista Horizonte, Sección 2, in vibrant Tijuana, Mexico.  Nestled in a prime location within this growing community, the home offers the perfect blend of affordability, customization, and proximity to the U.S. border. As an international realtor based in the United States, I am thrilled to present this unique chance to invest in a rapidly growing real estate market while securing a home that truly reflects your style.  A Home Ready for Your Vision  This newly constructed property is built to last, with a sturdy block foundation, and is immediately habitable. In keeping with the smart and cost-effective building practices in Mexico, this home is delivered ready for you to impart your personal style. The interior awaits your choice of paint, flooring, and a kitchen designed to your exact specifications. This is not a \"fixer-upper\" in the traditional sense, but rather a pristine, untouched space offering a unique opportunity to create the home of your dreams without paying for finishes you would have replaced anyway.  An Unprecedented Value Proposition  The Tijuana real estate market is experiencing a dynamic upswing, yet property prices remain significantly lower than in Southern California. This presents a golden opportunity for savvy buyers to acquire a brand-new home and build equity in a flourishing market. The cost savings extend beyond the initial purchase, with the finishing touches allowing you to control the budget and select materials that align with your financial goals.  Vibrant Area Highlights Within a 20-Mile Radius  Your new home in Vista Horizonte is strategically located to take advantage of the best of Baja California. A short drive unlocks a world of culture, entertainment, and culinary delights:  Cultural Experiences: Immerse yourself in the arts at the iconic Tijuana Cultural Center (CECUT), with its IMAX dome and fascinating museum. Explore the vibrant stalls of Mercado Hidalgo and Mercado El Popo for a true taste of local life. Entertainment & Sports: Catch a thrilling soccer match at Estadio Caliente, home to the Xolos, or enjoy a concert at one of the city\'s many venues. Beaches & Recreation: The beautiful shores of Playas de Tijuana and the lively seaside town of Rosarito Beach are well within reach, offering opportunities for surfing, horseback riding, and simply soaking up the sun. For family fun, Parque Morelos offers a zoo, paddleboats, and green spaces. Culinary ...', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/7lTQAxErgAR1uQjwdXNksinWTcuSwCD5lmC8LgWKvUY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/VPxJG9-gSzRftlXkSNr4Ak-Upr2n7Q-bBDVC0AKpYQs\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/86B1RAbRVFy9QiRla92KrfgvPzWO3Zn4UyFMIk8NK94\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/AY5F8qIRyl6rJl-W97zsDqycuW1v_Sa3xrTzCwKcVUQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/uoFijqHTwUTMMDh_nbIXe9sWDdapV3ph9s1ZacpeMOY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/T3-yTPmOxpdwdYclyfpItxzvd13jtO3t-pepxjhllGA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/saZi7hTE2v5Igful-kFQyUPDpUt4KvWDl6B1OlNTLrA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/thYeJh7RjxqEjJagqgSgEleRv7AD9ZosifaUgarlRm4\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117761978\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDAwNTUyMg\\/lxrTmZRZhbGwrsqe_oDdd7u_5