(1140, '1117747729', '1117747729', '2720 Klondike Way', '93222', '', 'Klondike', 'Pine Mountain Club', 'CA', 'Residential', 'ManufacturedOnLand', 2, 2.0, '8276', 0, 'One', 210000, 1296, '2026-02-02 15:33:42', '2025-06-18', 34.854789000000000, -119.172604000000000, 'Julia', 'Pickslay', 'Active', 'Real Brokerage Technologies, Inc', 'For over 50 years, this cherished home in Pine Mountain Club has been a vibrant backdrop for a family of six, a true \"time capsule\" from the 1970s filled with a lifetime of joyful memories.\r\r\n\r\r\nImagine generations of kids excitedly piling into the car, bound for adventures, escaping the rush of the LA lifestyle. Days were spent gold-panning, dreaming of striking it rich. Afternoons were filled with friendly matches on the tennis courts or the golf course, followed by refreshing dips in the community pool. Winters brought a magical transformation, with laughter echoing as snowmen were built and snowball fights waged. Every season offered an invitation to simply enjoy nature, from hiking scenic trails to stargazing.\r\r\n\r\r\nThis beloved double-wide mobile home, a comfortable 2-bedroom, 2-full bathroom abode, stands ready for new stories to unfold. Situated on an expansive 8,276 sq ft lot, there\'s an abundance of outdoor space just waiting for your personal touch. Picture cultivating your dream garden, or adding a play structure where future generations can create their own cherished memories. And to make your transition seamless, this charming retreat comes with furnishings included, so you can start living the Pine Mountain Club dream from day one.\r\r\n\r\r\nAre you ready to write your own family\'s story in this timeless mountain escape?', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117747729\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3MDA3NTc3Ng\\/22y2qNjW5KN8nrSyr4c0jfWpr41iZFbbiaxYdIQlg5o\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117747729\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc