(1185, '1117708583', '1117708583', '216 Jesse Road', '92285', 'Not Applicable-1', 'Jesse', 'Landers', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 0, 0.0, '217800', 0, '', 69900, 240, '2026-03-06 17:06:45', '2025-06-18', 34.282544000000000, -116.426013000000000, 'Patrick', 'Schmidt', 'Active', 'Sharon Rose Realty, Inc.', 'Mid Century flat-roof Homestead cabin set on 5 acres with views, utilities, & road access. Private setting just 2 streets away from hundreds of government open space land for hiking, dog walking & horseback riding. Zoned RL-5 which may allow for limited camping, 2 homes, guest homes & jr guest homes. Ideal for creating your dream compound. Many new designer homes in the area. Hot vacation destination with close proximity to the Integratron, Giant Rock, Johnson Valley & endless wilderness trails & canyons. Landers is seeing more celebrities, artists & musicians calling the area home than ever before. Inspiring vistas of the towering signature mountain that dominates the landscape. Views of the Bighorn Mtns, Landers, Mtn, & the Bullion Mtns that often glow red in the last light of the day. Shimmering city lights at night. Enjoy a peaceful campfire with friends under the vast milky way. About 1 hour to Big Bear & Palm Springs. 25 minutes to Joshua Tree National Monument where about 3 million tourists visit annually. 2.5 hours to LA. Short trip to organic restaurants, cafes, bars & shopping. The world famous music venue Pappy & Harriets is nearby in Pioneertown. For all questions & uses with Homestead cabins, buyers must contact the county. For all questions on utilities buyers must contact the utilities agencies. Address is not an assigned address & is for marketing purposes only. GPS: 34.282417, -116.425980 APN: 0629-322-16 Don\'t Wait! - Call Now!', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117708583\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3Mjg0NjAxNA\\/Rn-XgvN8HI-YJgae5PPtiic_sMbjfYBgjcNVW0HPTZM\",\"https:\\/\\/