(1305, '1118413709', '1118413709', '892 Toro Canyon Road', '93108', '', 'Toro Canyon', 'Santa Barbara', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 3, 7.0, '422968', NULL, 'One,MultiSplit', 10750000, 6415, '2025-12-21 09:37:04', '2025-06-17', 34.446329000000000, -119.559423000000000, 'Cristal', 'Clarke', 'Active', 'Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices California Properties', 'Located in a tranquil corner of Toro Canyon with sweeping views, just moments from Montecito and Summerland, this extraordinary 9-acre estate offers a rare blend of privacy, architectural pedigree, and natural beauty. A newly reimagined sanctuary, the property features a striking main residence and a charming guesthouse, thoughtfully placed amid lush landscaping and expansive outdoor living areas. Completed in 2025, the main residence reflects a curated fusion of Modernist and Japandi influences, all brought to life under the vision of renowned architect Robert \'\'Bob\'\' Easton. Inside, calm sophistication reigns. The spacious living room is anchored by a dramatic 17-foot slat-vaulted, open-beam ceiling, a sculptural fireplace, and sliding doors opening to a pergola-covered terrace.Portuguese limestone floors and slate-gray plaster walls set a serene tone throughout the main level. The gourmet kitchen is appointed with sleek black granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and top-tier stainless appliances. Nearby, an approximately 500-bottle temperature-controlled wine room offers both convenience and luxury. Both the primary and secondary bedrooms feature spa-inspired ensuite baths, generous closets, and access to multiple pergola-shaded terraces-each designed to invite indoor-outdoor living at its finest. Outdoor highlights include a sparkling infinity-edge pool, in-ground spa, built-in Wolf BBQ, and an alfresco dining area-all perfectly suited for entertaining or quiet repose. Enhanced by advanced home automation and fire prevention systems, this exceptional estate is where modern serenity meets timeless California style.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/Sy6wLWMaeaUPBpZyXHYoF8D1mbkWeuKI-uZ7hEKFA5M\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/K1W5Bpdbpgw69XNdg8ngr_FY6Jz8Xk0zZ_d88qSGAjo\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/g-RqQI0nrtH-UbvSVfuNJ-9Fy5NWOsb1Ras4UVcumqI\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/UJ_NPKspdvL9I_4qMvS4Wnaxm3lLm6dgR4wz-3JEPio\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/7n1zLM-Hnrc4ZiVBgv2wsG7Yb_mDgGiRZL-ieX5-D_8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/uQW5dK7JMDjFEOx6t5FknIiNPH_vhcBlxMgoEhoAxao\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/NLlp8PNWgUAE3YFgUuecup3rtOqKhLrKuTbr1HuHa98\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/JtrioBaaMILtdHQ6qPKa-9tkiodsXfyzrUOpamZYTDo\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/HVt3CL5bXaX5RjRa9ec0uFcd0FfxpYdbyUlPRUn2858\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/10\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2NjMzODkzNw\\/7zGPeZ-9DQ48-MFRV3_hqvGSVm9OB_9jiZnpO_LOjsA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1118413709\\/11\\/ODU2My84NTc1Lz