e space for potential additions like casita, swimming pool, or extra home. Conveniently located in peaceful  neighborhood, just 1.5 mile from Walmart Super Center shopping center, ensuring easy access to shopping and daily necessities. This gem of a home, is particularly appealing for investors, or buyers looking to create multi-generational living arrangements, rental properties, or personal recreational spaces like pool for leisure. Yucca Valley offers a serene lifestyle with easy access to natural attractions like Joshua Tree National Park, about 30 minutes  to Palm Springs, ideal for relaxations and convenience. Area is recognized for its arts community, stargazing tours opportunities, and growing residential appeal, making it an attractive destination for both, permanent residents and seasonal visitors.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/-E8MXErZ64QCCBiJ9PpSh72A3_ooA2fonajFon6GDw8\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/hjUEexV_f5mrEuHSLGknhN8FrdE9Pd-F-8u1s55g6rA\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/176TVCsW4vLBsCHpbBE-NCypIBjitQjauJyv-zSBhxg\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/qtMF04oUTg0BX5dc6Y19M_g8WWN-rx_x8oNZS9ACFQ0\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/qSVvVyc2vSC-mMB401nfz__YGvJKAJgh8dYZQCbqQnQ\",\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117718198\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDcyMjYxMQ\\/-SHTxYllIKngvfqU60HZzOAxU1HT4oYAy-geNnYJBbo\",\"http