(1325, '1117711226', '1117711226', '4162 Sullivan Road', '95338', '', 'Sullivan', 'Mariposa', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 2, 1.0, '87120', 0, 'One', 174900, 924, '2026-04-13 16:14:42', '2025-06-17', 37.432873000000000, -119.929037000000000, 'Henry', 'Vega', 'Active', 'Enrique Henry Vega Jr. Broker', 'Welcome to 4162 Sullivan Rd, a unique gem tucked in the beautiful foothills of Mariposa. This inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bath home offers 924 sq ft of cozy, well-designed living space on a generously sized fenced lot—perfect for those seeking comfort, privacy, and room to grow. Step inside and enjoy the light-filled open floor plan, where the spacious living room flows seamlessly into the connected kitchen, creating the perfect environment for entertaining or quiet nights at home. Large shutter-style windows provide character and allow you to control natural light and airflow with ease, adding charm and functionality to every room.The outdoors is where this property truly shines. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening wine on the backyard patio deck, or host summer barbecues in the designated sitting areas surrounded by nature. The fenced yard offers a safe and secure space for pets and children to play freely, while a handy shed provides extra storage for tools, bikes, or hobbies. Whether you\'re an outdoor enthusiast or just love fresh air, you\'ll fall in love with the nearby hiking and biking trails that make every weekend an adventure. Imagine living where natural beauty meets daily convenience.This home is also a great choice for families, with schools nearby and a warm, small-town community vibe that makes Mariposa such a special place to call home. For investors, this property offers strong potential as a vacation rental, long-term rental, or second home due to its desirable location, low maintenance footprint, and proximity to Yosemite National Park.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117711226\\/1\\/ODU2M