(1538, '1117457289', '1117457289', '70138 Sullivan Road', '92277', '', 'Sullivan', '29 Palms', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 4, 2.0, '108900', 0, 'One', 800000, 2825, '2026-03-24 11:27:39', '2025-06-16', 34.127861000000000, -116.132880000000000, 'Allison', 'Flatt', 'Active', 'Compass', 'Private desert estate on 2.5 acres with pool, spa, solar, and panoramic views! Ideal for second home, retreat, or high-end vacation rental. Located in one of the most desirable areas of Twentynine Palms, It\'s no secret why this property is highly rated & always booked! With EXECELLENT management at a favorable 12% rate and a prime location in a community of upscale luxury homes *BEL AIR OF 29 PALMS!* Enjoy modern amenities such as a solar-heated pool, NEW hot tub, and a woodstove that efficiently heats the entire house. Whether you\'re looking for your next STR or paradise to call home, come take a look, you won\'t be disappointed! The ultimate blend of seclusion and convenience with this meticulously curated 2,825 sqft desert retreat sitting on 2.5 acres. Enhanced by a permitted garage conversion to a spacious family room, this home offers a versatile den that can easily transform into a 5th bedroom, optimizing its appeal as a (STR) with a 12-person occupancy. Enjoy effortless ownership with this turn-key property, sparing you the high costs and challenges of renovations. The property has CONSISTENT weekend bookings ALL YEAR reflecting its popularity. Just minutes from grocery stores and a short walk to Joshua Tree National Park, the home offers 360-degree sunrise and sunset views, a vibe of serene isolation, and efficient solar panels to REDUCE the high cost of electricity. SOLD FULLY FURNISHED! The upscale, eclectic decor, curated with unique antiques and high-end consignment finds, sets this home apart. This property is a RARE GEM, ready to welcome its new owner with MINIMAL effort and MAXIMUM enjoyment.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Prop