ures`, `SpecialListingConditions`, `InteriorFeatures`, `PatioAndPorchFeatures`, `PoolFeatures`, `CommunityFeatures`, `SecurityFeatures`, `SpaFeatures`, `LotFeatures`, `ListingTerms`, `Disclosures`, `EntryLocation`, `OccupantType`, `RoomType`, `PhotosChangeTimestamp`) VALUES
(1593, '1117447246', '1117447246', '62177 Jericho Way', '92252', '', 'Jericho', 'Joshua Tree', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 1, 1.0, '54450', NULL, 'One', 449000, 432, '2025-10-11 12:57:20', '2025-06-16', 34.155191000000000, -116.306883000000000, 'Hannah', 'Pilkington', 'Active', 'Compass', 'ATTENTION! TWO AIRBNB INCOMES AND LAND TO BUILD MORE! Nestled on 1.2 acres of untouched desert beauty, this property features a fully remodeled main house plus a beautifully restored vintage Airstream - both thriving, top-rated Airbnb rentals with incredible reviews. Together, they present a rare dual-income opportunity. Set 75 feet apart and separated by sleek metal fencing, each dwelling has its own private driveway and entrance for maximum privacy. Both are being sold completely furnished, with everything included. The main residence was taken down to the studs and reimagined in 2021. It features a modern kitchen, stylish living area, spa-like bathroom, contemporary fixtures, and solar power. Step outside to a resort-style backyard with a luxurious pool, custom infinity deck, hot tub, firepit, BBQ grill, hammock, sun loungers, dining area, and even an outdoor shower - perfect for entertaining or unwinding. The Airstream has also been meticulously renovated and offers all the comforts of home, including a king-sized bed, two A/C units, WiFi, TV, induction cooktop, fridge, microwave, sink, and coffee maker. Outside, you\'ll find a private turf-covered lounge space with its own hot tub, cowboy pool, outdoor shower, dining area, BBQ, loungers, and a dedicated private bathroom. Located just five minutes from downtown Joshua Tree and the entrance to Joshua Tree National Park, this peaceful and private retreat offers a once-in-a-lifetime investment opportunity and a chance to live the dreamy desert lifestyle.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api-trestle.corelogic.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117447246\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2MDIxNDI3Nw\\/5FuH3NF