(1676, '1117435454', '1117435454', '19 Rippling', '92603', '', 'Rippling', 'Irvine', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 5, 3.0, '9152', NULL, 'Two', 2999000, 2769, '2026-04-10 22:32:57', '2025-06-15', 33.646663000000000, -117.809278000000000, 'Rose', 'Ferraro Fahey', 'Active', 'Compass', 'Experience timeless California living in this beautifully remodeled private pool home in the coveted Turtle Rock community. Thoughtfully updated throughout, the residence features a redesigned kitchen with new appliances, a new roof and lighting and fresh exterior paint with a 100-year warranty. The light-filled first floor offers seamless flow from formal living and dining areas to a cozy den/great room.  Both the living room and den/great room feature inviting fireplaces that add warmth and charm. Sliders open to a sparkling, redone pool perfect for effortless indoor-outdoor entertaining. A spacious first-floor primary suite and private office/bedrom provide comfort and flexibility. Upstairs, three additional bedrooms and an upgraded bath complete the home.  HOA Amenities include an HOA pool, tennis courts and hiking trails.  Enjoy close proximity to UC Irvine, Concordia University, scenic parks and premier golf courses in one of Irvine\'s most desirable neighborhoods.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117435454\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTg4NTg0OA\\/B3pJFoY35RomsQCmSwne6cRp5h1soD5l8_UKW-dVx_U\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117435454\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTg4NTg0OA\\/blElroH-dkwHCfPnrYRfP7s-ycCCfrA4xMhTGpih0PA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117435454\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTg4NTg0OA\\/YV-RqcikRzrzwLR_xom4ZlY2_hHgd-iO-yUXmDqwX20\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117435454\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc3NTg4NTg0OA\\/ap9DP-gt1RN