(1679, '1117430000', '1117430000', '7551 Hunters Valley Road', '95338', '', 'Hunters Valley', 'Mariposa', 'CA', 'Residential', 'SingleFamilyResidence', 5, 4.0, '28.77', 2, 'Two', 1499900, 5188, '2026-01-11 18:06:11', '2025-06-15', 37.579132000000000, -120.173243000000000, 'Jenifer', 'Canter', 'Active', 'Realty Concepts, Ltd.', 'Exquisite Estate House, CHARMING SFR COTTAGE, DARLING STUDIO, TRAVERTINE, HARDWOOD FLOOR AND CURATED ARTISAN FINISHES.  FULLY FENCED, DRIP-IRRIGATED VIA WELL-FED YEAR ROUND POND, ESTABLISHED AGRICULTURAL USE AND EQUESTRIAN CAPABLE.  \r\r\nExperience a comfortable refined Manor in the Foothills of Yosemite with almost 7000 sq ft (between three living areas) at the Lyons Vineyard Estate.  Remarkable 28+ acre TWO HOME AND STUDIO compound just 15 minutes from historic Mariposa and about an hour from Yosemite Main Gate. This rare property has natural beauty, perfect private retreat, award winning boutique vineyard, successful rental, and extensive horseback riding.  Pan for gold in your private stream, throw in a private airport supporting substantial private aircraft just out of hearing distance and this is a GEM. The particulars: Main Estate House 5188 sqft. Completely remodeled from frame out in 2008 w/travertine, hardwood, granite and artisan finishes. The curated contents of exceptional taste include Waterford Chandeliers, fine artwork, classy furnishings and are negotiable. This is an unparalleled turn-key offering. The Charming SFR Cottage 960 sq ft 2bd/1ba and 600sf detached garage. Cute 704sf Studio w/bathroom is attached to a 4-vehicle carport and ideal for a conversion to bunkhouse, extra family visitors, or Vinter.  \r\r\nEight acres of mature award winning grapes, four each Cab and Syrah professionally maintained with a drip irrigated well-fed pond. The wine cellar is located in the main residence and holds over 1800 bottles. Enjoy your exceptional red wine on several balconies while stargazing or watching friends ride. The Estate has been home to horses for many years and​​‌​​​​‌​​‌‌​​‌​​​‌‌​​​‌​​‌‌​‌‌‌​‌​​​‌‌​ fenced.', '[\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/1\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/Ae8OMzjgiVhYioG-2c3CCBPcXxowFXXINcwpQsqj_k8\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/2\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/XfVQ6eouS5wyydeArqOL2aHWU_tbkYv5WPX-R9cN2XY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/3\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/t9IT1f8kO-qAfE_KKyMNP3rEp8L-CPGZhEumyAc1Luk\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/4\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/RUQ9mBL26B7IqOz5uuXIVHM4jWqDT7Y80SAUQ1b7VEE\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/5\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/ZhywlygmGSGKqPHT4-XMdjsYWnWdOOq4kSNZP-ay2tY\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/6\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/GBPCHFKXLc1pn8-HgZuX8EGhGx0WobVPMYFqrwOZiZw\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/7\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/Ps5-q3b5g0XSZDT6IVKj0Ig2l19Nb2TmhLa2-fLnbfA\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/8\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/8Smbz2aZ89spr_u11SIa2Zd3mvooEN9Q7kwSjoDMK0g\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/9\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/CvYadFjhDxxb98RJ0lCJZF-jUmvurwbeqI_5_DXhoko\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Media\\/Property\\/PHOTO-Jpeg\\/1117430000\\/10\\/ODU2My84NTc1LzIw\\/MjAvMTcwMjMvMTc2ODE4NDAzNQ\\/QmwpxL23RH_l4GHY_2WKQEybIWqVjD7nUXoFEYeqRsM\",\"https:\\/\\/api.cotality.com\\/trestle\\/Medi